  "notes": "OPEN QUESTION for the Salesforce-side team: if a promotion is supposed to give a product the shopper did NOT add, this API does not express it. That scenario would need a custom mechanism. The adapter keeps a BasketHelper.addBonusProduct utility for that case, but the standard GPM response does not drive it."
